      <title>花旗前中国首席经济学家因银行裁员而离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/citigroup-s-ex-china-chief-economist-exiting-as-bank-cuts-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，花旗集团财富部门亚太经济分析主管、前首席中国经济学家刘利刚即将离职，该银行在大规模重组中开始了新一轮全球裁员。此事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/citigroup-s-ex-china-chief-economist-exiting-as-bank-cuts-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 05:00:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
